            "description": "In Singapore, CFOs in the Asia-Pacific region are increasingly embracing artificial intelligence, as revealed in the latest 2026 Future Ready CFO Survey - APAC Regional Insights. The survey highlights that CFOs are acknowledging AI's significant impact on finance operations and are actively integrating it in a strategic and value-centric approach. A substantial 83% of CFOs in the Asia-Pacific region see the adoption and utilization of AI as a crucial factor reshaping finance, aligning closely with the global average of 85%.",
